Sentencas: The electrochemical properties of La2NiO4+delta electrodes were investigated as a function of the electrode thickness based on three-electrode half cells.
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: The electrocatalytic activity of the electrodes with the varied thicknesses ranging from 5 to 30 mu m was surveyed by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy technique under open-current voltage conditions.
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: The cathodic polarization curves of these electrodes were also inspected.
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: The results indicated that the electrochemical properties of these electrodes were highly dependent on their thickness.
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: The polarizations of involved electrode reaction processes displayed different variations with changing the electrode thickness.
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: Tuning the electrode thickness was confirmed to be effective for optimizing the electrochemical properties.
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: Among the investigated electrodes, the electrode with a thickness of similar to 20 mu m achieved the optimal properties.
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C in air, this electrode exhibited a polarization resistance of 0.24 Omega cm(2), an exchange current density of 201 mA cm(-2) and an overpotential of 40 mV at 200 mA cm(-2).
Titulo: Optimization on the electrochemical properties Of La2NiO4+δ cathodes by tuning the cathode thickness

Sentencas: On this ground, an anode-supported single cell with similar to 20 mu m thick La2NiO4+delta cathode was fabricated.

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C and using hydrogen fuel, this single cell attained a maximum powder density of 500 mW cm(-2).
